  "text": "As a consequence, ND systems have been primarily studied within the framework of philosophical logic, being widely used in teaching (but again, mostly in the philosophy curriculum) and have been ignored by the automated theoremproving community, where research has mostly concentrated on purely analytic methods such as resolution and tableau based approaches [CITATION_1] .",
